#

Pumpkin Seed Oatmeal

15 min
$2.5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastHealthyQuickNutritious

Description

A hearty and nutritious oatmeal topped with crunchy pumpkin seeds and a hint of spice, perfect for a cozy breakfast.

Ingredients

  • rolled oats: 1 cup
  • water or milk: 2 cups
  • pumpkin seeds: 1/4 cup
  • maple syrup or honey: 1-2 tablespoons
  • cinnamon: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: a pinch
